Nollywood actor and filmmaker, Kunle Afolayan in a throw back picture he shared today, you know it’s TBT, advised his followers to make the best use of every moment. Probably remembering what he shared in the past with late Moji, Kunle posted the above photo captioning it;

‘Some years back with the beautifully talented @bimboakintola and the adorable late #mojiolaiya . Make the best of now as no one knows what the next Sec holds. #throwbackthursday #throwback’.

May her soul continue to rest in peace. Amen!
